[
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-5789_57158_000013_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/5789/57158/5789_57158_000013_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-5789",
        "content": "A FIT COMPANION,--FOR ME AND MY SISTERS.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-slow_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "very slow",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-5789_57158_000014_000007",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/5789/57158/5789_57158_000014_000007.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-5789",
        "content": "But on this Wednesday he received a letter, and,--as he told himself, merely in consequence of that letter,--he called at the attorney's house and asked for Miss Masters.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-5789_57158_000015_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/5789/57158/5789_57158_000015_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-5789",
        "content": "\"I have brought you a letter from my aunt,\" he said.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-slow_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-5789_57158_000016_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/5789/57158/5789_57158_000016_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-5789",
        "content": "I am so glad.\"",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-slow_e-high",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-5789_57158_000017_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/5789/57158/5789_57158_000017_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-5789",
        "content": "\"She was writing to me and she put this under cover.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-normal_e-high",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-5789_57158_000017_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/5789/57158/5789_57158_000017_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-5789",
        "content": "I know what it contains.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-low_s-slow_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-5789_57158_000017_000002",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/5789/57158/5789_57158_000017_000002.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-5789",
        "content": "She wants you to go to her at Cheltenham for a month.\"",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-normal_e-high",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-5789_57158_000019_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/5789/57158/5789_57158_000019_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-5789",
        "content": "\"Would you like to go?\"",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-5789_57158_000020_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/5789/57158/5789_57158_000020_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-5789",
        "content": "\"How should I not like to go?",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-slow_e-high",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-5789_57158_000020_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/5789/57158/5789_57158_000020_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-5789",
        "content": "Lady Ushant is my dearest, dearest friend.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-5789_57158_000023_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/5789/57158/5789_57158_000023_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-5789",
        "content": "\"Why not go?\"",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-slow_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "very slow",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-5789_57158_000024_000003",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/5789/57158/5789_57158_000024_000003.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-5789",
        "content": "If the old lady had altogether kept Mary it might have been very well; but she had not done so and mrs Masters had more than once said that that kind of thing must be all over;--meaning that Mary was to drop her intimacy with high born people that were of no real use.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-low_s-slow_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-5789_57158_000024_000006",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/5789/57158/5789_57158_000024_000006.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-5789",
        "content": "\"I don't think it will be possible, mr Morton.\"",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-normal_e-high",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-5789_57158_000028_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/5789/57158/5789_57158_000028_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-5789",
        "content": "\"What do you mean by that, mr Morton?\" she asked blushing up to her hair.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-slow_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-5789_57158_000028_000002",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/5789/57158/5789_57158_000028_000002.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-5789",
        "content": "Ever since that walk her mind had been troubled by ideas as to what he would think about her, and now he was telling her what he thought.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-low_s-slow_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-5789_57158_000032_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/5789/57158/5789_57158_000032_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-5789",
        "content": "\"Of course I shall answer her.\"",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-fast_e-high",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "fast",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-5789_57158_000033_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/5789/57158/5789_57158_000033_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-5789",
        "content": "\"Perhaps you can let me know.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-5789_57158_000034_000002",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/5789/57158/5789_57158_000034_000002.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-5789",
        "content": "I can explain it all to her and she will understand me.\" She hardly meant to reproach him.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-slow_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-5789_57158_000034_000004",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/5789/57158/5789_57158_000034_000004.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-5789",
        "content": "But he felt that she had reproached him.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-slow_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-5789_57158_000037_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/5789/57158/5789_57158_000037_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-5789",
        "content": "Then it seemed as though there were nothing else for him but to go;--and yet he wanted to say some other word.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-slow_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-5789_57158_000039_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/5789/57158/5789_57158_000039_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-5789",
        "content": "\"If I did think that,--that-\"",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-slow_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "very slow",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-5789_57158_000040_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/5789/57158/5789_57158_000040_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-5789",
        "content": "\"It does not signify in the least.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-normal_e-high",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-5789_57158_000040_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/5789/57158/5789_57158_000040_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-5789",
        "content": "I only want Lady Ushant to understand that if I could possibly go to her I would rather do that than anything else in the world.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-5789_57158_000040_000002",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/5789/57158/5789_57158_000040_000002.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-5789",
        "content": "Because Lady Ushant is kind to me I needn't expect other people to be so.\" Reginald Morton was of course the \"other people.\"",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-5789_57158_000041_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/5789/57158/5789_57158_000041_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-5789",
        "content": "Then he paused a moment.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-low_s-slow_e-high",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-5789_57158_000041_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/5789/57158/5789_57158_000041_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-5789",
        "content": "\"I did so long,\" he said, \"to walk round the old place with you the other day before these people came there, and I was so disappointed when you would not come with me.\"",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-low_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-5789_57158_000042_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/5789/57158/5789_57158_000042_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-5789",
        "content": "\"I was coming.\"",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-slow_e-high",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "very slow",
        "energy": "very high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-5789_57158_000043_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/5789/57158/5789_57158_000043_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-5789",
        "content": "\"But you went back with-that other man.\"",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-slow_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-5789_57158_000044_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/5789/57158/5789_57158_000044_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-5789",
        "content": "What was I to do?",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-5789_57158_000047_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/5789/57158/5789_57158_000047_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-5789",
        "content": "\"I didn't say so at all.\"",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-low_s-normal_e-high",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "very high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-5789_57158_000050_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/5789/57158/5789_57158_000050_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-5789",
        "content": "\"I don't say that.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-slow_e-high",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "very high",
        "speed": "very slow",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-5789_57158_000050_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/5789/57158/5789_57158_000050_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-5789",
        "content": "But as you were too grand for our friend of course you were too grand for us.\"",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-5789_57158_000052_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/5789/57158/5789_57158_000052_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-5789",
        "content": "\"You don't think that, mr Morton.\"",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-slow_e-high",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-5789_57158_000054_000002",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/5789/57158/5789_57158_000054_000002.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-5789",
        "content": "He had come there ardently wishing that she might be allowed to go to his aunt, and resolved that he would take her himself if it were possible.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-low_s-normal_e-high",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-5789_57158_000054_000003",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/5789/57158/5789_57158_000054_000003.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-5789",
        "content": "But now he almost thought that she had better not go.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-slow_e-high",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-5789_57158_000054_000005",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/5789/57158/5789_57158_000054_000005.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-5789",
        "content": "If she meant to marry mr Twentyman what good could she get by associating with his aunt or with him?",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-low_s-slow_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-5789_57158_000055_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/5789/57158/5789_57158_000055_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-5789",
        "content": "After that he walked straight out to Bragton.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-slow_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-5789_57158_000055_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/5789/57158/5789_57158_000055_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-5789",
        "content": "He was of course altogether unconscious what grand things his cousin john had intended to do by him, had not the Honourable old lady interfered; but he had made up his mind that duty required him to call at the house.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-low_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-5789_57158_000055_000002",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/5789/57158/5789_57158_000055_000002.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-5789",
        "content": "So he walked by the path across the bridge and when he came out on the gravel road near the front door he found a gentleman smoking a cigar and looking around him.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-5789_57158_000055_000003",
