        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-5789",
        "content": "Good afternoon to you, sir.\" Then Reginald having thus done his duty returned home.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-low_s-slow_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "very low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-5789_57195_000005_000005",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/5789/57195/5789_57195_000005_000005.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-5789",
        "content": "In all that misery the poor attorney had the worst of it.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-5789_57195_000005_000006",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/5789/57195/5789_57195_000005_000006.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-5789",
        "content": "Mary was free from her stepmother's zeal and her stepmother's persecution at any rate at night;--but the poor father was hardly allowed to sleep.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-low_s-slow_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-5789_57195_000005_000015",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/5789/57195/5789_57195_000005_000015.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-5789",
        "content": "In all these disputes he never quite yielded.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-low_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-5789_57195_000006_000004",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/5789/57195/5789_57195_000006_000004.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-5789",
        "content": "If Mary must go to Cheltenham, why could she not go by herself, second class, like any other young woman?",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-low_s-slow_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-5789_57195_000007_000002",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/5789/57195/5789_57195_000007_000002.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-5789",
        "content": "Her letter to Mary, though affectionate, was very short.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-normal_e-high",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-5789_57195_000008_000002",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/5789/57195/5789_57195_000008_000002.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-5789",
        "content": "She was not excellent herself at the writing of letters, and therefore she got Dolly to be the scribe.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-low_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-5789_57195_000011_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/5789/57195/5789_57195_000011_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-5789",
        "content": "Your affectionate friend,",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-5789_57195_000013_000007",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/5789/57195/5789_57195_000013_000007.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-5789",
        "content": "He wrote a scrawl to Dolly,--\"I'll come,\" and, having sent it off by the messenger, tried to trust that there might yet be ground for hope.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-low_s-slow_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "very low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-5789_57195_000014_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/5789/57195/5789_57195_000014_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-5789",
        "content": "She had no new argument to offer,--except this last interposition of Providence in her favour.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-low_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-5789_57195_000017_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/5789/57195/5789_57195_000017_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-5789",
        "content": "\"It has all been put off.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-slow_e-high",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-5789_57195_000017_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/5789/57195/5789_57195_000017_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-5789",
        "content": "She shan't go at all if I can help it.\"",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-low_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-5789_57195_000018_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/5789/57195/5789_57195_000018_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-5789",
        "content": "\"But why has it been put off, mrs Masters?\"",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-low_s-slow_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-5789_57195_000019_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/5789/57195/5789_57195_000019_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-5789",
        "content": "\"Lady Ushant is coming to Bragton.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-slow_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-5789_57195_000024_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/5789/57195/5789_57195_000024_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-5789",
        "content": "He stood for awhile scratching his head as he thought of it.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-slow_e-high",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-5789_57195_000031_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/5789/57195/5789_57195_000031_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-5789",
        "content": "\"That's why I speak open to you.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-slow_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "very slow",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-5789_57195_000031_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/5789/57195/5789_57195_000031_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-5789",
        "content": "Don't you be afraid of her.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-normal_e-high",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-5789_57195_000033_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/5789/57195/5789_57195_000033_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-5789",
        "content": "I say there ain't nobody;--nobody.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-5789_57195_000033_000002",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/5789/57195/5789_57195_000033_000002.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-5789",
        "content": "If anybody tells you that it's only just to put you off.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-normal_e-high",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-5789_57195_000033_000003",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/5789/57195/5789_57195_000033_000003.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-5789",
        "content": "It's just poetry and books and rubbish.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-slow_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "very slow",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-5789_57195_000033_000004",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/5789/57195/5789_57195_000033_000004.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-5789",
        "content": "She wants to be a fine lady.\"",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-slow_e-high",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-5789_57195_000034_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/5789/57195/5789_57195_000034_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-5789",
        "content": "\"I'll make her a lady.\"",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-low_s-slow_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
